    <main class="main-content">
        <header class="top-bar">
            <h3>Operations Manual</h3>
            <div class="search-container">
                <input type="text" class="search-input" placeholder="Search SOPs (e.g. 'Drive Upload', 'Wiring Invoice')...">
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="dashboard-grid">
            
            <!-- SECTION 1: FIELD SOPs (The Daily Grind) -->
            <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 2;"> <!-- Full width -->
                <h2>Daily Field Workflows</h2>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-title">1. Arrival & Pre-Scan</div>
                        <p>Check in with shop manager. Connect VCI. Perform full health scan using OEM software preferred.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-title">2. Photo Documentation (Google Drive)</div>
                        <p>Required photos: VIN Plate, Cluster (Engine Running), Damage Area, Setup (Targets in view).</p>
                        <a href="#" style="color:var(--primary-color)">View Detailed Photo SOP ></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-title">3. Calibration & Post-Scan</div>
                        <p>Perform cal. Verify light is out. Perform post-scan. Upload screenshots to Drive folder `[RO_Number]`.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 2: INSURANCE PRICING (Searchable Table) -->
            <div class="card" style="grid-column: span 2;">
                <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
                    <h2>Insurance Pricing Guidelines</h2>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Filter by Carrier..." style="padding:5px;">
                </div>
                <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:#666; margin-bottom:15px;"><em>Last Updated: Jan 02, 2026</em></p>
                
                <div class="table-container">
                    <table class="data-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Insurance Carrier</th>
                                <th>Hourly Rate</th>
                                <th>Scan Flat Rate</th>
                                <th>Notes / Restrictions</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>State Farm</strong></td>
                                <td>$XXX.XX</td>
                                <td>$XX.00</td>
                                <td>Requires pre/post scan output files attached to final invoice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>Geico</strong></td>
                                <td>$XXX.XX</td>
                                <td>$XX.00</td>
                                <td>Use "Sublet" code 4921. No markup allowed on parts.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td><strong>Allstate</strong></td>
                                <td>$XXX.XX</td>
                                <td>$XX.00</td>
                                <td>Contact adjuster for approval if > 2.0 hours.</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 3: SOFTWARE STACK (The How-To) -->
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Software & Apps</h2>
                <!-- Tabs for Software Categories -->
                <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom:15px;">
                    <button style="margin-right:15px; font-weight:bold; border:none; background:none;">Production</button>
                    <button style="margin-right:15px; color:#999; border:none; background:none;">Admin/HR</button>
                    <button style="color:#999; border:none; background:none;">IT/Support</button>
                </div>
                
                <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom:10px;"><a href="#"><strong>OPUS / Map Scrub</strong></a><br><small>Billing codes & map report generation.</small></li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom:10px;"><a href="#"><strong>CCC One</strong></a><br><small>Writing estimates and supplementing.</small></li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom:10px;"><a href="#"><strong>Google Drive</strong></a><br><small>Naming convention: `YYYY-MM-DD_RO_Last6VIN`.</small></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 4: WIRING & REPAIR -->
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Wiring & Repairs</h2>
                <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom:15px;">
                        <strong>Best Practices</strong><br>
                        <a href="#">Solder vs Crimp Guide</a> | <a href="#">Heat Shrink Standards</a>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom:15px;">
                        <strong>Parts Catalog</strong><br>
                        <a href="#">View Van Stock List (Terminals/Seals)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Invoicing Wiring</strong><br>
                        <span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:#666;">Bill as "Labor - Mechanical". List connectors as separate line items.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
	<script src="../script.js"></script> <!-- or src="../script.js" if inside /pages/ folder -->
